15 club, the name of the business owner, and shall state:
16 (A) That the manager, or in the case of a bed and
17 breakfast private club or a hotel, restaurant, or large-event facility
18 private club, the owner, at least one (1) partner, or the majority
19 stockholder is a citizen of Arkansas;
20 (B) That he or she is of good moral character;
21 (C) That he or she has never been convicted of a felony or
22 had a license to sell or dispense alcoholic beverages revoked within the five
23 (5) years preceding the date of the notice; and
24 (D) That he or she has never been convicted of violating
25 the laws of this state or of any other state governing the sale or dispensing
26 of alcoholic beverages.
