Subtitle
15
16 TO AMEND THE LAW REGARDING ALCOHOLIC
17 BEVERAGES; AND TO REMOVE THE REQUIREMENT
18 THAT A PRIVATE CLUB BE A NONPROFIT
19 ORGANIZATION.
